INSERT INTO bundle_drafts (trainerId, title, description, price, cadence, status, imageUrl, goalsJson, servicesJson, productsJson) VALUES 
(1, 'Full Body Transformation', 'Complete 12-week fitness program with nutrition guidance, personal training sessions, and premium supplements.', '299.99', 'monthly', 'published', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1534438327276-14e5300c3a48?w=800', '["Build lean muscle", "Improve endurance", "Develop healthy habits"]', '{"sessions": 8, "checkIns": 4, "deliveries": 2}', '[]'),
(1, 'Yoga for Beginners', 'Start your yoga journey with this beginner-friendly program including weekly sessions and guided meditation.', '149.99', 'monthly', 'published', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544367567-0f2fcb009e0b?w=800', '["Improve flexibility", "Reduce stress", "Build core strength"]', '{"sessions": 4, "checkIns": 2, "deliveries": 1}', '[]'),
